# Keep source tex files
!*.tex

# =========================
# LaTeX build folders
# =========================
paper/build/
paper/_minted*/
_minted*/

# =========================
# Optional: ignore compiled PDFs
# 如果你想把最终 PDF 也传到 GitHub，就注释掉下面两行
# =========================
paper/*.pdf
*.pdf

*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.synctex.gz

# 但保留最终论文 PDF
!paper/Aapmcm26203797.pdf
# =========================
# Excel temporary files
# =========================
~$*.xlsx
~$*.xls

# =========================
# Data policy
# =========================
# 默认不忽略 data，因为比赛项目可能需要保留数据。
# 如果 merged.xlsx 很大或不想公开数据，可以取消下面两行注释：
# data/
# *.xlsx

# =========================
# Reports / exported tables
# =========================
report/*.xlsx
report/*.csv
problem/*.xlsx
problem/*.csv
temp/